parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the electric power steering can cause the steering wheel to lock up, making it difficult or impossible to control the vehicle, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The power steering assist fault message is displayed
the steering wheel becomes hard to turn or locks up
the vehicle is difficult to control
the power steering fails suddenly
the vehicle is unable to steer.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the throttle body can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to a loss of control and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or loses power
the wrench light or check engine light comes on
the vehicle surges or jerks
the accelerator pedal feels stuck or spongy
the vehicle goes into limp mode.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The unintended acceleration of the vehicle can cause loss of control, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The vehicle accelerates without warning
the brake pedal is depressed but the vehicle does not stop
the vehicle surges or jerks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The stalling of the engine can cause loss of control, leading to accidents and injuries.
symptoms: The engine stalls or dies
the vehicle loses power
the wrench light or check engine light comes on.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the rear brake light can cause other drivers to be unaware of the vehicle's intention to stop, increasing the risk of rear-end collisions.
symptoms: The rear brake light does not illuminate when the brake pedal is pressed
or it remains illuminated even when the brake pedal is not pressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The interference between the headlights and brake lights can cause the brake lights to remain illuminated even when the brake pedal is not pressed, leading to confusion for other drivers and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: The brake lights remain illuminated when the headlights are on
even when the brake pedal is not pressed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the LED tail lights can cause the vehicle to fail safety inspections and increase the risk of accidents due to reduced visibility.
symptoms: The LED tail lights fail to illuminate or flicker intermittently.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash can result in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag did not deploy in a crash
the airbag warning light is illuminated.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delay in repairing the Takata airbag recall can lead to a prolonged risk of injury or death due to the faulty airbag.
symptoms: The dealer does not have the parts to repair the airbag
the manufacturer has not provided a timeline for the repair
the recall notice has been received but the repair cannot be scheduled.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The airbag system fault can lead to the failure of the airbag to deploy in a crash, resulting in serious injury or death.
symptoms: The airbag warning light is illuminated
the airbag system is showing fault codes
the crash sensor is faulty.
